Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙到底打算讓我等多久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底在做些什麼才會浪費這麼多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為那傢伙已經離開多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:01:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整整三天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經無奈得無話可說了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙到底是有多磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那傢伙還被村裡的人當做眼中釘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣慢吞吞地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再遇上些什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了 是要給媽媽穿的婚紗…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸是不是為了找那個花了太多時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 就算如此他也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的壽命也沒有那麼長以至於讓他浪費時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你想想 爸爸說會一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是說了他願意一直和你在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽你不覺得幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 時間永遠不會前進的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種世界 會是什麼感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說呢 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:11.95,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0}act 10 空想forest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種地方居然有房屋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明這麼近為什麼至今為止都沒有人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是奪走了槻彥的怪物的妖術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是槻彥說那隻怪物是自己的老婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物是槻彥的老婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙肯定是被怪物的妖術操縱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它操縱槻彥之後 打算今後襲擊村子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成那樣的話事情就難辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我們一起上 速戰速決
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你磨磨蹭蹭什麼呢 快點走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…感覺剛剛好像聽見了腳步聲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爸爸回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是槻彥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我一口氣痛射了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這傢伙是怪物的女兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:29.87,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這頭髮…絕對沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 把這傢伙一起幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂 這傢伙不是還小嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在磨磨蹭蹭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了 我親自來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目隱」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼 她居然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…是妖術？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目覺」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先…先撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目欺」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目奪」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目合」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲起來也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你們逃到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能立刻知道你們的藏身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槻彥他怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你執意不說的話那我就直接讀取你的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目盜」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快點把操縱你的怪物的所在之處告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也是不想揍你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們不能放著來歷不明的東西不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薊是我的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要對她…出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 為什麼你要包庇那隻怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你還要反抗的話 我可不會手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在包庇她 我不是全都告訴你們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我的家人永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 有一些類似標記的東西好像一直延續到森林方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 槻彥這傢伙為了回去好像做好了準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上做好降服怪物的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也該醒醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能降服了那傢伙你也能醒過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快點做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底對我做了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後不要再帶任何人到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了的話 就快點給我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槻彥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑 不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再靠近我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再因為我而傷害你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無視天道 甚至將你們無端捲入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其實早就已經發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為有我存在所以才會失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要沒有我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就可以如我所願幸福地生活在這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我不奢求幸福的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想做個美夢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個能與家人永遠生活在一起的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很愛你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你們的愛無以復加
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑 你不是什麼怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不要使用這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我可能沒有資格說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你要作為一個人類和你父親幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就是 我的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要走 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永遠都愛著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永遠都會祈禱 你們能夠幸福地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說過不行啊 茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又想一個人偷偷跑出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…外面看上去很好玩的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 不要說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽念故事給你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 當然可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就來這邊和媽媽一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就講這個故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從媽媽消失留下我們的那天直到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底過了多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管父親去世的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是茉莉出生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽都沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽她是否依舊一個人在那個無法終究的世界裡獨自生活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一人等待著也許某天就會回來的媽媽就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等茉莉再長大一些 就讓她看看外面的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界一定會接納這個孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像媽媽對我說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在茉莉的幸福就是我的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 不知道什麼時候睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 你在的話就快點回應我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怪物好像不止一隻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼久遠的故事到現在還有什麼可信度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 拜其所賜我們也找到了些有趣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看她的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果做成展品給人看的話 可是能大賺一筆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個 快點放開那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你個怪物在那裡說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要吵 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 要不要把她也抓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你聽我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是…沒能…獲得幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到是你故意把她們拉進來 你也不是什麼好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個永遠無法完結的世界的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是最為了解的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我怎麼能閉嘴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順從一己之利尋求安逸的慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而創造了這個世界的人不就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來你的願望原本就是帶著摯愛的家人來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這樣不就非常好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母女還有孫女三人能夠相見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的願望終於實現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你是多麼愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯 就是要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那利己主義 和其他相比才能帶給我們最高的快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑 一切…都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這表情真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招致這一切悲劇的原因就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少…也要讓這個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然自己主動放棄了女王蛇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果它能夠成功寄宿的話 應該會變成那孩子的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這樣 能夠抑制這個世界的人就不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄宿於你體內的蛇因為女王的消失又會如何狂躁不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不會讓你留下寂寞的回憶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這個世界內所下達的「吞噬8月15日逝去的生命」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一指示再也無人能夠阻止呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 我就不應該離家出走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就是修哉不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為修哉總是對人家惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又自動地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 你和家人走散了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…可能也和你一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那雙紅紅的眼睛也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 再也不能走散了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救…我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是…女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了我的眼睛就會變成石頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成石頭…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 我必須要一個人待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你快點回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「救救我」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼喚我的人就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 我也和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人也總是非常害怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用害怕也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡著了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 那個孩子去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丟下我一個人就跑去別的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣會感冒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我好渴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不燙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不燙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是從哪裡來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要在那種地方睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是忘事先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘事先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也經常忘記一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:20:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我想如果我能記住很多事情就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只記得一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…想要朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要…和朋友一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋…友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我只記得這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…只想和朋友一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 你就和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜歡和我做朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能介紹我的朋友給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家肯定也很樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在已經是深夜零點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是請看這擁堵的人群
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直難以置信 到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如觀眾所見 現場變得很混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊 我聽得見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一定都在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女失去了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:22:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常 非常重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.38,0:23:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女一個人哭泣著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想再和大家一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女反覆如此祈禱著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎有什麼對少女說道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就讓你的願望實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就讓你的期望成真吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就給予你一個能實現你的空想的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(203,231.5)\bord0\fs27\shad2}act11:賞月recital
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受…受夠了 這種世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.41,0:23:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的內心 生命 理想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在願望面前都是無價值的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瘋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:42.38,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}夏風がノックする窓を開けてみると
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:46.89,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}何処からか迷い込んだ鳥の声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:54.22,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}読みかけの本を置き　「何処から来たんだい」と笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:58.09,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}目隠ししたままの午後三時です。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:04.98,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}世界は案外シンプルで複雑に怪奇した
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:09.35,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}私なんて誰に理解もされないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:16.81,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}街外れ、森の中、人目につかないこの家を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:20.58,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}訪れる人などいない訳で。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:27.51,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}目を合わせないで！　固まった心、一人ぼっちで諦めて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:31.92,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}目に映った無機物（もの）に安堵する日々は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:39.30,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}物語の中でしか知らない世界に少し憧れる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:44.06,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}ことくらい許してくれますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:51.14,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}タンタン、と鳴り響いた心の奥に溢れてた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:56.76,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}想像は世界に少し鳴り出して
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:18:02.50,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}ねぇねぇ、突飛な未来を教えてくれたあなたが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:09.12,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}また迷ったときはここで待っているから。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:42.38,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}夏風敲著門 當我試著打開窗戶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:46.89,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}不知何處傳來了迷途鳥的鳴叫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:54.22,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}放下正在閱讀的書 「是從哪裡傳來的呢」笑著說道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:58.09,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}蒙上眼睛 已經是下午三點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:04.98,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}世界意外如此單純  複雜被視為怪異
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:09.35,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}誰也無法理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:16.81,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}遠離街市 森林之中 這個不起眼的家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:20.58,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}當然不會有人來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:27.51,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}不要和我的視線相對！ 已經凝固的內心 獨自一人已斷念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:31.92,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}只有無機物日復一日地映入眼簾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:39.30,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}稍微憧憬著從書中獲知的外界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:44.06,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}僅僅是這種程度的事可以被允許嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:51.14,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}鐺鐺的響聲 已經從內心深處溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:56.76,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}想像的世界漸漸敲響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:18:02.50,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}吶吶 將未知的未來告訴我的你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:09.12,INCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}在我迷惘的時候 還會在這裡等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}コンクリートが揺らいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:21.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}霞み燻む、君の望ている夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}テンプレートをなぞった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}知らないままの日常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:28.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}ハイテンポなアテンダンス
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:31.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}消えない　足りない　落ち込んだ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:33.53,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}最終話が来たって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}言えない　君は泣きそう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:37.36,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}ほら、目を閉じて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:38.81,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}迷子なら一緒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:40.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}帰り道もないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:44.03,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}継ぎ接いでた　秘密に願う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:45.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}未来は平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:47.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}さぁ、手を鳴らせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:51.45,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}０で廻った　勘違いを今日も集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:52.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}君もまた、無我夢中？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:56.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「play」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:57.82,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}届くまで叫んで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:58.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「save」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.69,0:01:00.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}叶うまで足掻いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:02.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}その手を掴むまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:05.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}この温度は忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:05.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「daze」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.50,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}心を消さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:08.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「change」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}一人で泣かないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:12.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}「孤独」なら　塗り替えれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:17.85,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}「ひとりぼっち」を変えようとした君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.14,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}混凝土震顫著的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:21.65,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}籠罩在霞光中的 你一直看著的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.79,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}點綴著範式的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.76,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}依然一無所知的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:28.65,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}快速參與其中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:31.30,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}不會消失 無法滿足 消沉的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:33.53,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}最終話就要到來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.79,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}說不出這句話的你泫然欲泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:37.36,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}來 閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:38.81,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}我們迷途之人應當一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:40.79,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}你也沒有歸宿之處對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:44.03,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}不斷接續著 悄悄地許願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:45.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}未來是平凡的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:47.06,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}來 擊掌為證
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:51.45,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}今天也從零開始聚集一切誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:52.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.39,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}你是否也迷途夢中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:56.16,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「play」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:57.82,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}吼叫到傳達給你為止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:58.61,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「save」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.69,0:01:00.27,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}掙扎到實現為止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:02.66,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}直到緊握住那隻手為止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:05.22,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}我不會忘記這份溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:05.86,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「daze」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.50,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}不要消卻真心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:08.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「change」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.08,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}不要獨自哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:12.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}「孤獨」什麼的 是可以重寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:17.85,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}與想要不再「一人獨處」的你在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:28.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}意味のないままで　期間は過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:38.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}理解しようとして　気づいた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:46.04,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}遠く離れた笑え声なんも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:52.98,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}どこにも聞こえない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:58.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}涙が落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:03.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}これが未来だというならいっそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:08.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}やりきってない明日を手放して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:14.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}声の聞こえない場所に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:18.56,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}一人でいよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.76,0:22:23.65,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}暮れる世界の涙を知って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:29.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}溢れ出す理不尽を数えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:45.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}こんな日々を　おくる意味はきっと見つけられないなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:28.20,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}毫無意義的日子裡 期限卻已過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:38.01,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}想要去理解 卻察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:46.04,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}分隔在遙遠之地的笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:52.98,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}在哪裡也聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:58.35,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}眼淚都落下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:03.86,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}如果這就是未來的話 還不服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:08.68,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}果敢地放棄還沒有到來的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:14.53,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}在聽不見聲音的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:18.56,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}一個人靜一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.76,0:22:23.65,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}就算知道逝去世界的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:29.35,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}就算列舉溢出的荒謬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:45.73,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}這樣度過每一天的意義 最後也一定不會找到
